               <title type="main">
The <normalised orig="Naturall" auto="true">Natural</normalised> Mans Case stated, or, An exact map of the little world man, Considered in both his Capacities, Either in the state of nature, or grace, As is laid down in XVII sermons, By that late <normalised orig="truely" auto="true">truly</normalised> Orthodox Divine, Mr. Christopher Love, Pastor of Lawrence Jury, London. Whereunto is annexed The Saints Triumph over Death; Being his funeral sermon, By that painful Labourer in the Lords Vineyard, Mr. Tho. Manton, Minister of the <normalised orig="Gospell" auto="true">Gospel</normalised> at Stoak-Newington near London.
