pride is apt to grow in the best mans<lb/>
heart, and therefore God would have us<lb/>
sometime look back upon what we were<lb/>
in our unconverted estate, that so that<lb/>
might abate the pride of our spirits: you<lb/>
have an excellent place for this in<lb/>
Ezek. 16.3,4,5. compared with the last<lb/>
verse of that chapter. <normalised orig="Sayes" auto="true">Says</normalised> God there to<lb/>
